title: Vincent van Gogh The Bedroom Paint Tube Pen
description:
Paint tube pen developed from Vincent van Gogh’s The Bedroom, 1889, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

It may look like a tube of paint, but when the top is taken off it reveals a pen tip.  Comfortable grip for writing.  Has a small image of Vincent van Gogh’s The Bedroom, 1889, on the tube’s wrap.

  • Dimensions:  4.33 x 1.25 x .86 in.
  • Ink Color:  Black Ink
